This is demo project for Jersey which used filtering to handle exception.

Here is the steps to test. (Used Postman REST Client)

1. Enter 'http://localhost:8080/JerseyDemoFilter/demo/login' without Authentication values

2. 'This request requires HTTP authentication' Response should display with 401 error 

3. Again enter 'http://localhost:8080/JerseyDemoFilter/demo/login' with Authentication values

4. " welcome !"  message should display as response